---
import Icon from './Icon.astro';
---

<section class="box skills">
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="terminal-window" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Virtualization & Compute</h2>
		<p>Architecting and managing high-availability (HA) compute clusters using Proxmox VE. Deploying, isolating, and orchestrating containerized workloads with Docker and LXC across Linux and Windows Server environments.</p>
	</div>
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="strategy" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>Network & Security</h2>
		<p>Designing secure network topologies with strict VLAN segregation and core infrastructure services (DNS/DHCP). Implementing Zero Trust remote access (Wireguard/Tailscale) and managing traffic flow via reverse proxies (Nginx, HAProxy)</p>
	</div>
	<div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
		<Icon icon="list" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
		<h2>IT Operations & Storage</h2>
		<p>Administering Active Directory for identity management and provisioning resilient ZFS storage arrays with automated snapshots. Managing cross-platform file sharing (NFS/SMB) and foundational cloud infrastructure across AWS and GCP.</p>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.box {
		border: 1px solid var(--gray-800);
		border-radius: 0.75rem;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		background-color: var(--gray-999_40);
		box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
	}

	.skills {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 3rem;
	}

	.skills h2 {
		font-size: var(--text-lg);
	}

	.skills p {
		color: var(--gray-400);
	}

	@media (min-width: 50em) {
		.box {
			border-radius: 1.5rem;
			padding: 2.5rem;
		}

		.skills {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
			gap: 5rem;
		}

		.skills h2 {
			font-size: var(--text-2xl);
		}
	}
</style>
